{"tid":1308744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九龍公路鐵枝炒起變炮彈 插入CID車探員險死","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T03:36:51.000Z","uid":267309,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"50b351a396f6a32ff090a8b0af0d43d6e6031475","tid":1308744,"uid":267309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"深水埗港鐵南昌站對開發生驚險交通意外，今早(12日)9時11分，一名便衣探員駕駛一輛屬於警方的私家車，沿西九龍公路往尖沙咀方向行駛，期間疑有車輛輾過路面一條約1.3米長的鐵枝，引致鐵枝飛起，先擊中探員駕駛的私家車車頭冚及車牌，繼而再彈起，鐵枝斜插入擋風玻璃，幸探員及時閃避，僅手部被打中受傷。探員立即緊急停車及報警。警方正展開調查，列作「交通意外有人受傷」。<br />\n<br />\n受意外影響，西九龍公路出尖沙咀交通受阻，龍尾至葵涌八號貨櫃碼頭。<br />\n<br />\n鐵枝飛插入私家車內。（陳賜慧攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/bkn-20190712093955496-0712_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fbkn-20190712093955496-0712_00822_001.html&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0DBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=feb47d84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/bkn-20190712093955496-0712_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3eeea2c1b7ba3d299ba7130a908d990675a0795b","tid":1308744,"uid":267309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:28:25.000Z","msg":"未死,大家為警察打氣"},{"pid":"35ec8656648c44c7c06cf57c7bc0ce48e6563a4e","tid":1308744,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>聽日去上水 三個一齊推 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[突發][713光復上水]一封北區居民寫給香港人的公開信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307753\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307753</a><br />\n<br />\n！！緊 急 ！！突 發！！上 水 連 儂 牆 要 人！ ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308369\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308369</a><br />\n<br />\n［抗爭支線］！七 月 十 三 ！光 復 上 水 ！踢 走 水 貨 客！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307559\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307559</a><br />\n<br />\n洗唔洗開兩個Post呀"},{"pid":"931b5a6244ced1d0aa376ca517af5916